1.4
log
@Call the FreeS/WAN sysdep 'freeswan'. The 'linux' sysdep will be native Linux IPSec.
@
text
@#	$OpenBSD: Makefile.sysdep,v 1.3 2002/06/10 18:08:59 ho Exp $

